    <h4>Overview</h4>
    <p>The <code>&lt;c:PEG_Message_CMP&gt;</code> component is a pure display utility
        component to be used in other components.</p>
    <p>It enables do display a message (a title + optional detailed content) in various
        variants (info,warning...) and handles all the mapping of icons and colours.</p>
